# Superchain-Ops Repository Structure

## Task Organization
- Tasks are organized under `src/improvements/tasks/<network>/<task-number>-<description>/`
- Networks include: `eth/` (Ethereum mainnet), `sep/` (Sepolia testnet), etc.
- Each task directory contains: `README.md`, `config.toml`, `.env`, `VALIDATION.md`

## Key Template Files
- [src/improvements/template/OPCMUpgradeV300.sol](mdc:src/improvements/template/OPCMUpgradeV300.sol) - Template script for OPCM v3.0.0 upgrades
- [src/improvements/template/OPCMUpgradeV200.sol](mdc:src/improvements/template/OPCMUpgradeV200.sol) - Template script for OPCM v2.0.0 upgrades

## Execution Guides
- [src/improvements/SINGLE.md](mdc:src/improvements/SINGLE.md) - Guide for single safe execution
- [src/improvements/NESTED.md](mdc:src/improvements/NESTED.md) - Guide for nested safe execution
- [src/improvements/single.just](mdc:src/improvements/single.just) - Justfile for single safe tasks
- [src/improvements/nested.just](mdc:src/improvements/nested.just) - Justfile for nested safe tasks

